article:
This is an incomplete list of landmarks in Manhattan from 14th Street to 59th
Street designated by the New York City Landmarks Preservation Commission. Some
of these are also National Historic Landmark (NHL) sites, and NHL status is
noted where known.

: source: [http://www.nyc.gov/html/lpc/html/forms/reports_man.shtml];
:[http://www.neighborhoodpreservationcenter.org/designation_reports/]; date
:listed is date of designation;

:see also: [[National Register of Historic Places listings in Manhattan from
14th to 59th Streets]]
categories: Locally designated landmarks in the United States
